        ": إذا التق المؤمنانِ كان بينهما مائة رحمة؛ تسع وتسعون لأشَدّهما حباً لصاحبه"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.muhajir-b-ali": [
          "57. It has been reported that Abu 'Abd Allah (a.s) said: When two believers meet, one hundred mercies are showered between them—ninety nine of these go to the one who loves the other more."
